cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.SY, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on plan synthesis for multi-agent systems.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with task specifications and plan synthesis, which are common topics in AI.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper uses linear temporal logic formulas to specify tasks.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with modeling agents as discrete state-transition systems.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper proposes an iterative algorithm for plan synthesis.
